title: The Future Sound of London Studio Discography [FLAC]
description:
Part 1 of a 4 part series compiling the works of Brian Dougans and Gary Cobain, known to most as the Future Sound of London. This torrent contains the most definitive collection of studio works under the Future Sound of London moniker I could compile.

Please note: All of the audio in this torrent was ripped to FLAC with the exception of the recent EP, A Gigantic Globular Burst of Antistatic, which was only sold online in MP3 format.
